            Businesses
        

Lazard has a simple and powerful model, focused on two businesses: Financial Advisory and Asset Management.








Financial Advisory

We advise clients around the world on strategic and financial matters including mergers and acquisitions, restructurings, capital structure and capital raising.


Learn More








Asset Management

We manage investment portfolios in key regions of the world and distribute them locally, regionally and globally.


Learn More











"Clients turn to Lazard because they have known us for years—or decades. They know we can achieve outcomes they couldn’t achieve otherwise."






Kenneth M. Jacobs
Chairman and Chief Executive Officer








Our Clients

We have Financial Advisory clients in more than 70 countries. They include corporations, partnerships, institutions, governments, sovereign entities and individuals. Our Asset Management business serves a diverse global client base that includes pensions, sovereign wealth funds, governments, corporations, financial institutions and high-net-worth individuals. 







Our Alliances

Lazard enters into select joint ventures and strategic alliances to serve our clients and broaden our network of relationships. 


Lazard Korea






























